data.description: Welcome to this charming and meticulously maintained home located in a desirable neighborhood. This beautiful property offers 4 bedrooms 2.5 Bathrooms and almost finished basement, making it an ideal place for a growing family or those looking for additional space. The updated kitchen boasts modern appliances, plenty of storage space, and stylish countertops. Whether you are a seasoned chef or simply enjoy cooking, this kitchen will surely inspire your culinary skills.  The bedrooms are generously sized, allowing for comfortable living and privacy. Step outside to the amazing deck, where you will find a beautifully landscaped yard and a patio area, perfect for hosting summer barbecues or enjoying your morning coffee. Conveniently located near all major grocery stores and 316 Hwy, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. With a easy access to Five Forks Park and Alexander Park, families will appreciate the outdoor recreational activities. Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience all the amazing features and charm this property has to offer.
